1. *Dovoljan* broj ljudi se prijavio za kurs (A *sufficient* number of people applied for the course)
2. Nije *dovoljna* hrana za sve goste (There is not *enough* food for all guests)
3. Oni su mi *dovoljno* platili za taj posao (They paid me *enough* for that job)
4. *Dovoljno* je važno da učite strane jezike (It is *sufficiently* important to learn foreign languages)
5. Želim da kupim *dovoljno* knjiga za letovanje (I want to buy *enough* books for the vacation)
6. Ako *dovoljno* ranije dođemo, uspećemo da dobijemo dobre karte za pozorište (If we come *early enough*, we will manage to get good tickets for the theatre)
7. *Dovoljno sam* umoran da idem na spavanje (I am *sufficiently* tired to go to sleep)
8. *Dovoljno su* lepe ove slike (These pictures are *quite* beautiful)
9. Ima li *dovoljno* mesta za sve nas u automobilu? (Is there *enough* space for all of us in the car?)
10. Da li je *dovoljno* jasno o čemu se radi? (Is it *sufficiently* clear what is going on?)